{"vocabInfos":[{"lsjDefs":"<b> περιμένω</b>, <br /> <b>wait for, await</b>, with <i>accusative</i> <i>person</i>, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th c.BC: Herodotus Historicus 4.89, 5th-6th c.BC: Aristophanes Comicus “Plutus” 643, etc.; π. Τισσαφέρνην ἡμέρας πλείους ἢ εἴκοσι 5th-6th c.BC: Xenophon Historicus “Anabasis” 2.4.1, etc.: with _accusative_ _of things_, π. ἐξ ἀγορᾶς ἰχθύδια 5th-6th c.BC: Aristophanes Comicus “Fragmenta” 387.8 \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]; τοῦ καιροῦ μὴ περιμένοντός τι as the time could not <b>wait for</b>.., [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 1st-2nd c.AD: Plutarchus Biographus et Philosophus “Caesar” 17. \">Refs 1st c.AD+</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__2</b></Level3> <b>require, expect</b>, σχολάζουσαν φιληκοΐαν [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] 2.172e. \">Refs</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__3</b></Level3> <b>endure, put up with</b>, μακρὰ λέγοντας ἡμᾶς αὐτοὺς περιεμείναμεν [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th-6th c.BC: Plato Philosophus “Leges” 890e. \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]<br /><Level3><b>__4</b></Level3> of events, <b>await, be in store for</b>, τίς με πότμος ἔτι π.; [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th c.BC: Sophocles Tragicus “Antigone” 1296 (Lyric poetry)\">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]; μὴ θύσαντας δεινὰ π. [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 5th-6th c.BC: Plato Philosophus “Respublica” 365a; ἃ τελευτήσαντα ἑκάτερον π. [prev. work] 614a. \">Refs 5th c.BC+</a>]<br /><Level2><b>__II</b></Level2> with <i>infinitive</i>, οὐ περιμενοῦσιν ἄλλους σφᾶς διολέσαι <b>will</b> not <b>wait for</b> others to destroy them, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\"[prev. work] 375c \">Refs</a>]; ἕκαστος [τῶν λόγων] π. ἀποτελεσθῆναι <b>awaits</b> its accomplishment, [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" [prev. author] “Tht.” 173c \">Refs</a>]; μηδ᾽ ἐφ᾽ ἑαυτὸν [τὰ τοιαῦτα] ἐλθεῖν π. [<a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" title=\" 4th c.BC: Demosthenes Orator 21.220; π. τὰ λοιπὰ μαθεῖν 1st c.BC: Dionysius Halicarnassensis 1.13. \"